What is an API Key?

An API Key is like a password that identifies your application.

Without an API Key

Your App
   ❌
Cannot talk to OpenAI

With API Key

Your App
     │
API Key
     │
OpenAI Server
     │
AI Response

Example

sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

Never share your API key publicly.
